{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ecf-api-collection-v1",
    "name": "ECF API — Facturación Electrónica RD",
    "description": "Colección completa para la API SaaS de facturación electrónica (e-CF) para República Dominicana.\n\n## Primeros pasos\n1. Importar también `ecf-api.postman_environment.json`\n2. Llenar las variables `base_url`, `tenant_email`, `tenant_password`\n3. Ejecutar **Auth > Login** para obtener el token\n4. Ejecutar **Auth > Crear API Key** y guardar en la variable `api_key`\n\n## Autenticación\nTodos los endpoints (salvo Login y Register) requieren el header:\n```\nX-API-Key: {{api_key}}\n```\n\n## Documentación\nSwagger en: `{{base_url}}/docs`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "api_key", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "API key — llenar después de ejecutar Auth > Crear API Key" },
    { "key": "tenant_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "company_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "buyer_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "invoice_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "webhook_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sequence_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "apikey",
    "apikey": [
      { "key": "key", "value": "X-API-Key", "type": "string" },
      { "key": "value", "value": "{{api_key}}", "type": "string" },
      { "key": "in", "value": "header", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Autenticación y gestión de API Keys",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/tenants/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["tenants", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Mi Empresa Integradora\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@miempresa.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo tenant (cuenta) en la plataforma. Retorna las API keys iniciales de test y producción."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Has tenant ID', () => {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "  pm.expect(data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('tenant_id', data.id);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@miempresa.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Login con email y contraseña. Retorna JWT para el dashboard."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Has accessToken', () => {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "  pm.expect(data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', data.accessToken);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear API Key",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/keys", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "keys"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Integración ERP - Producción\",\n  \"isLive\": false,\n  \"scopes\": [\"FULL_ACCESS\"]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea una API key con scopes específicos. El valor completo solo se muestra una vez — cópialo a la variable `api_key`."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Has key value', () => {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "  pm.expect(data).to.have.property('key');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('api_key', data.key);",
                  "  console.log('API Key creada:', data.key);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar API Keys",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/keys", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "keys"] },
            "description": "Lista todas las API keys del tenant (muestra solo los últimos 4 caracteres de cada key)."
          },
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"] } }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Revocar API Key",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/keys/:id", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "keys", ":id"], "variable": [{ "key": "id", "value": "{{key_id_to_revoke}}" }] },
            "description": "Revoca una API key permanentemente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Rotar API Key",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/keys/:id/rotate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "keys", ":id", "rotate"], "variable": [{ "key": "id", "value": "{{key_id_to_rotate}}" }] },
            "description": "Revoca la key actual y crea una nueva con los mismos scopes."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tenants",
      "description": "Gestión del tenant (cuenta de la empresa integradora)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Ver Mi Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/tenants/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["tenants", "me"] },
            "description": "Retorna información del tenant actual."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "if (data && data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenant_id', data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Estadísticas del Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/tenants/me/stats", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["tenants", "me", "stats"] },
            "description": "Retorna estadísticas de uso: facturas emitidas, empresas, webhooks."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/tenants/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["tenants", "me"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Empresa Integradora Actualizada\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Companies",
      "description": "Empresas emisoras de e-CF",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear Empresa",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["companies"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"rnc\": \"130000001\",\n  \"businessName\": \"Empresa Ejemplo SRL\",\n  \"tradeName\": \"Empresa Ejemplo\",\n  \"address\": \"Av. Winston Churchill 1099, Santo Domingo\",\n  \"phone\": \"809-555-0100\",\n  \"email\": \"info@empresa.com\",\n  \"dgiiEnv\": \"DEV\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Registra una empresa emisora. El RNC se valida contra DGII. En DEV usa el ambiente de pruebas."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "if (data && data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('company_id', data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Empresas",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["companies"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "if (data && data.length > 0) pm.collectionVariables.set('company_id', data[0].id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver Empresa",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Empresa",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"809-555-0200\",\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@empresa.com\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar Empresa",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}"] },
            "description": "Soft-delete: desactiva la empresa pero conserva su historial."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Buyers",
      "description": "Clientes y compradores (directorio de contribuyentes)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear Comprador",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/buyers", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["buyers"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"rnc\": \"131793916\",\n  \"email\": \"contacto@cliente.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"809-555-0101\",\n  \"contactPerson\": \"Juan Pérez\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea un comprador. Si provees RNC, los datos se auto-completan desde DGII."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "if (data && data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('buyer_id', data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Compradores",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/buyers?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["buyers"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "buyerType", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver Comprador",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/buyers/{{buyer_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["buyers", "{{buyer_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Comprador",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/buyers/{{buyer_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["buyers", "{{buyer_id}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@cliente.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"809-555-0202\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh DGII",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/buyers/{{buyer_id}}/refresh-dgii", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["buyers", "{{buyer_id}}", "refresh-dgii"] },
            "description": "Vuelve a consultar DGII y actualiza razón social y estado del comprador."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Certificates",
      "description": "Certificados digitales .p12 para firma XMLDSig",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Subir Certificado",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}/certificates",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}", "certificates"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": \"{{company_id}}\",\n  \"p12Base64\": \"MIIKDgIBAzCCCcoGCSqGSIb3DQEHAa...\",\n  \"passphrase\": \"mi-password-del-certificado\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Sube el .p12 en Base64. Convierte: `base64 -i cert.p12` (macOS/Linux) o `[Convert]::ToBase64String([IO.File]::ReadAllBytes(\"cert.p12\"))` (PowerShell)."
          },
          "event": [
            { "listen": "prerequest", "script": { "exec": ["// Asegúrate de que p12Base64 tenga el contenido real del .p12 en Base64"] } },
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"] } }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Certificados",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}/certificates",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}", "certificates"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver Certificado Activo",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/companies/{{company_id}}/certificates/active",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["companies", "{{company_id}}", "certificates", "active"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna el certificado activo actual. 404 si no hay ninguno activo."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sequences",
      "description": "Secuencias de eNCF autorizadas por DGII",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear Secuencia",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/sequences", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["sequences"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": \"{{company_id}}\",\n  \"ecfType\": \"E31\",\n  \"startNumber\": 1,\n  \"endNumber\": 10000,\n  \"expiresAt\": \"2027-12-31T23:59:59.000Z\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Registra un rango de eNCF autorizado por DGII. Necesitas la autorización de la DGII (OFV) primero."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "if (data && data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('sequence_id', data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver Secuencias de Empresa",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/sequences/{{company_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["sequences", "{{company_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verificar Disponibilidad",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/sequences/{{company_id}}/available?type=E31",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["sequences", "{{company_id}}", "available"],
              "query": [{ "key": "type", "value": "E31" }]
            },
            "description": "Verifica si hay eNCF disponibles para el tipo de comprobante solicitado."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Anular Secuencias (ANECF)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/sequences/{{company_id}}/annul", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["sequences", "{{company_id}}", "annul"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ranges\": [\n    { \"encfFrom\": \"E310000000151\", \"encfTo\": \"E310000010000\" }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Anula eNCF no utilizados ante DGII mediante documento ANECF."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Invoices",
      "description": "Emisión y gestión de facturas electrónicas e-CF",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "E31 — Factura con Valor Fiscal",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/invoices", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["invoices"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": \"{{company_id}}\",\n  \"ecfType\": \"E31\",\n  \"buyer\": {\n    \"rnc\": \"131793916\",\n    \"name\": \"EMPRESA COMPRADORA SRL\",\n    \"type\": 1\n  },\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Servicio de consultoría tecnológica\",\n      \"quantity\": 1,\n      \"unitPrice\": 10000,\n      \"itbisRate\": 18\n    }\n  ],\n  \"payment\": {\n    \"type\": 1,\n    \"method\": 2\n  },\n  \"idempotencyKey\": \"{{$timestamp}}-E31-001\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "E31: Factura con Valor Fiscal para contribuyentes registrados. RNC del comprador es obligatorio."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Generar idempotency key único por request",
                  "pm.variables.set('timestamp', Date.now());"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 202 (encolado)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(202));",
                  "pm.test('Status QUEUED', () => {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "  pm.expect(data.status).to.equal('QUEUED');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('invoice_id', data.id);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "E32 — Consumidor Final",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/invoices", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["invoices"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": \"{{company_id}}\",\n  \"ecfType\": \"E32\",\n  \"buyer\": {\n    \"name\": \"Consumidor Final\",\n    \"type\": 2\n  },\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Producto para consumidor final\",\n      \"quantity\": 2,\n      \"unitPrice\": 500,\n      \"itbisRate\": 18\n    }\n  ],\n  \"payment\": {\n    \"type\": 1,\n    \"method\": 1\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "E32: Consumidor Final. NO requiere RNC. Monto total < RD$250,000 para ser válido."
          },
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('Status 202', () => pm.response.to.have.status(202));"] } }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "E33 — Nota de Débito",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/invoices", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["invoices"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": \"{{company_id}}\",\n  \"ecfType\": \"E33\",\n  \"buyer\": {\n    \"rnc\": \"131793916\",\n    \"name\": \"EMPRESA COMPRADORA SRL\",\n    \"type\": 1\n  },\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Ajuste por diferencia de precio\",\n      \"quantity\": 1,\n      \"unitPrice\": 2000,\n      \"itbisRate\": 18\n    }\n  ],\n  \"payment\": { \"type\": 1 },\n  \"reference\": {\n    \"encf\": \"E310000000001\",\n    \"date\": \"01-05-2026\",\n    \"modificationCode\": 3,\n    \"reason\": \"Corrección de monto factura original\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "E33: Nota de Débito. Requiere `reference` con el eNCF de la factura original."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E34 — Nota de Crédito",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/invoices", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["invoices"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
